docs {
  ## Update Experiment V2

  ID-based partial update. Only changed configs trigger selective re-run.
  All fields are optional — only send what changed.

  ### Request Body
  - `column_id` — Update ground truth column (no re-run)
  - `prompt_config` — Prompt/agent configs. Include `id` (from GET detail) to update existing; omit `id` to add new.
  - `user_eval_metrics` — Eval configs. Include `id` (from GET detail) to update existing; omit `id` to add new.

  Configs present in GET detail but omitted from the update payload are removed (soft-deleted).

  ### Response
  Returns updated experiment detail (same as GET detail).
}
